{
  "stem": "5356.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they burned the City Hall, which was about a mile away from that part.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the next couple of days, they assembled most of the people, men and-- only men, into a-- a hole, which was the fireman's hole, like where the theatres used to be played.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They assembled the people, and they kept them there till their random was paid for-- to let them out.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This was the first week when the Germans occupied the city.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father was taken in there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they spent there, I think about two days, they spent in there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then they released them after it was arranged with them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The city was also a powiat, which means like a district government.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It wasn't just a city government, it was also like-- here, I think you would call it a county.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The same thing that was a county.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was an impressive building in there where the-- then, when the Germans came in, they took over all those offices.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, and they were direct in their business.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then there was another part of the city-- that was where the [INAUDIBLE] were stationed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they-- they were the security.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then we had the SA-- SD.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Also those were security police.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the first few months, I mean, there was a lot of refugees streamed in from the east, from Kalisz, from Poznan, and from all those things.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And people from the biggest cities started coming in because where we were, food was no problem because the farmers were all around the city.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So you could-- the farmers were allowed to come in, even after they created the ghetto in 1941.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We couldn't go out, but the Poles could come in with their ware and sell.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
